{"type": "article", "id": 13833, "title": "自然竹椅子", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-21T08:09:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122445sA7megfjZar3JcQG.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一件来自 Milk Design 的竹椅子，设计师试图通过和传统工艺师的对接，能够把民间传统工艺的美好和时尚的现代家居结合在一起。椅子取材自自然生长的竹子，设计过程中保持竹子的外观性状，只进行切割和组装的处理，金镯组装方式让椅子充满现代感，带来更好的视觉效果，同时也使得现代设计和传统的手工艺和谐共存。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141507TjlS5koH0JsEn3MO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67083333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141508VXOYJZk4H8bumwBK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72083333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141509cQ74neaYmNJ0oOju.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141510CasXl5K0cE9LNRjA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141510zHu9NFtD0iK8eQcM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141511XIoMeP4tK23DGjvN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141512zOv5FCNdqJuW7eRT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141512jtQ1kghOPbIEnuxf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141513hAzL1Gy4F0oabPWs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}